title: Week 13 preview & Cowboys vs Vikings recap
itunes:title: Week 13 preview & Cowboys vs Vikings recap
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game previewing each week 13 matchup, and revealing which team is their “Lock of the Week”. Plus, the heroes recap the Thursday night game between the Cowboys and the Vikings.
